                    "title": "Job Description",
                    "content": "VCOM Inc. has immediate openings for Fibre Optic Technicians to work in San Jose and surrounding areas.<br/>Applicants must have a minimum of 2 years experience in fibre optic splicing and testing.<br/>We have been in business since 1998 and are privately owned Canadian Contracting Company that offers its' customers a wide range of services from Installations and Service, Construction, Technical, Planning & Design, Fibre Optics, Directional Drilling and much more.<br/>We offer competitive wages, benefits, Employee Retirement Plan and many more other perks.<br/>"
                },
