                    "title": "Qualifications",
                    "content": "<ul><li>Splice and test various types of fibre optic cable</li><li>Can read system maps</li><li>Can operate all types of splicing and testing equipment</li><li>Must be able to carry and climb a twenty eight foot extension ladder and the ability to work at heights</li><li>Must be well organized and able to work independently and or as part of a team</li><li>Will be required to work in all weather conditions</li><li>Will be required to work weekends and off hours</li></ul>"
